## Answers to Common Questions
- **What is ashwagandha?** An adaptogenic herb (Withania somnifera) used in Ayurvedic medicine for 3,000+ years to reduce stress and anxiety.
- **How long to see results?** Most users notice improved sleep within 2 weeks; stress relief typically within 4–8 weeks of daily use.
- **Is it safe for daily use?** Yes. KSM-66® is GRAS (Generally Recognised As Safe). Suitable for adults. Not recommended during pregnancy.
- **Are they vegan?** Yes — pectin base (fruit-derived), no gelatin, no animal ingredients.
- **What is the price?** ₹449 for a 15-day supply (30 gummies).
- **Do they contain sugar?** No — sugar-free formula sweetened naturally.
- **Where are they made?** Manufactured in India under GMP and ISO 22000 certified facilities.
